title: #067 – Goal Setting with Intention
itunes:title: #067 – Goal Setting with Intention
description:
If you’re ready to take your goal-setting to the next level this is the episode for you. Get ready to make REAL CHANGE in your life and business!

Looking for the BONUS worksheet for today’s episode? Click here. 

THINGS YOU’LL LEARN:  

  • The three step process for goal-setting that Alex swears by
  • How to stay committed & create a level of accountability
